{"type":null,"faqId":48077,"title":"更改声音设置","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178118\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“声音”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.  </span><span>在“声音”界面，您可以：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“音量”，调整音乐、来电、通知、闹钟或通话等的音量大小。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“静音模式”开关，开启或关闭静音模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“静音时振动”开关，开启或关闭手机静音时的振动效果。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“卡 1 来电铃声”或“卡 2 来电铃声”，分别设置两张卡的来电铃声。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“卡 1 来电时振动”或“卡 2 来电时振动”“响铃时振动”开关，分别设置两张卡的响铃时的振动效果。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“默认通知铃声”，设置通知铃声。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“系统”区域下的开关，开启或关闭手机的触摸、锁屏、拨号键盘等的提示音或振动效果。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3663","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598112000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":155,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}